Have you ever wanted to be the hero of your own story? With AI Dungeon, you can be. Roleplay in any scenario you can imagine, with artificial intelligence creating infinite possibilities for your character to interact with. Lead an army fighting back an alien invasion, or be a mythical detective investigating the attempted assassination of the fairy queen. Be the Dungeon Master in your own Dungeons and Dragons campaign. There are no limits to what you can do in AI Dungeon.

An experience only possible through AI.

AI Dungeon is the first ever artificially intelligent open-ended text-based role playing game (rpg) adventure game. It uses cutting edge artificial intelligence technology to generate infinite content on the fly, giving you a completely unique and dynamic experience every time you play. AI Dungeon is also the first app to use the Stable Diffusion in-app for image generation (similar to other AI image generators like Midjourney and Dall-e 2).

Define your world

In AI Dungeon, you can roleplay in any scenario or world you can imagine. Choose from predefined worlds created by other users, or create your own unique world using our quick start system. You can also use the AI generator to create a random world for you to explore.

Take Action

As the adventure's protagonist, you can decide what your character says or does. The AI will produce responses from the other characters or world events for you to respond to. Every adventure is unique and unexpected.

In AI Dungeon, you are the hero of your own AI story. With infinite possibilities at your fingertips, it's up to you to save the day.

Choose a Genre

With so many possibilities, it can be hard to decide what kind of adventure you want to go on. To help you choose, we've listed some of the most popular genres below. Pick your favorite and dive in!

Fantasy: In a fantasy world of magic and adventure, anything is possible. Will you save the princess from the dragon or overthrow the corrupt king?

Mystery: Use your detective skills to solve crimes and uncover conspiracies. Can you catch the killer before they strike again?

Zombies: Fight for survival in a world overrun by zombies. Will you become a hero or succumb to the infection yourself?

Apocalyptic: The world is ending. Can you find a way to survive?

Cyber Punk: In a future world of advanced technology and artificial intelligence, anything is possible. Will you save the world from the evil megacorporations or become a powerful CEO yourself?

The possibilities are endless in AI Dungeon. What will you do?

AI Dungeon was first thought of while Nick Walton played Dungeons and Dragons (dnd). They were playing through their campaign. Nick thought that there had to be a way to play this with AI. Now you can play a Dungeons and Dragons-esque game right from your phone.
